Name: Erdling
rawData:
Erdling (German for "Earthling") are a German Neue Deutsche Härte band founded in 2014 from former band members of the band Stahlmann.
The band members include Neill Freiwald (vocals, guitar, programming), Neno Knuckle (guitar), Christian Eichlinger (drums), and Robin Sem Vedrfölnir (bass guitar).
Singer Neill Freiwald

Genres: Neue Deutsche Härte, Dark Rock, German Rock
